songs.title: Hollow
songs.lyrics:
I don't think you really know
I can see how much you bled
Every night I spent with you
You were hanging by a thread

Cut through all your veins, yeah
I know you're in pain, yeah
Feel like you're all alone
I'm here please pick up the phone

Make me feel alright
Like I'm okay tonight
Like I can manage, I can heal
Please make me feel something real

Make me feel alright
Like I'm okay tonight
Like I can manage, I can heal
Please make me feel something real

Please make me feel something real
